                    "description": "I was the editor of the in 2014 published book \"De Koninklijke Luchtmacht in Nieuw-Guinea\" and of a book about foreign airplanes in Dutch service in World War I that was published in the Spring of 2016 under the title De Interneringen van vliegtuigen tijdens De Groote Oorlog; I wrote a booklet about the history of the Dutch Airforce Reserve. On November 22 2015 this book, \"Luchtmachtreservisten Toen & nu. Groep Luchtmacht Reserve 2004-2014\" was published and the first example was presented to the Inspector-General of the Dutch Armed Forces, lieutenant-general B.H. Hoitink in the National Military Museum at Soesterberg.\nIn the Spring of 2015 I was a member and Airforce specialist of the committee \"Evenement 75 jaar Slag om Ypenburg-Residentie\" that took place on May 9th-10th 2015. At the same time I edited the book Ypenburg 10 mei 1940. In the last few years I wrote some articles about the aviation history of The Hague in De Oud -Hagenaar/ Haagse Tijden. At this moment I try to get some decorations for the relatives of veterans who never received a decoration.",
